Package: chemodiv
Title: Analysing Chemodiversity of Phytochemical Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hampus", "Petrén", email = "hampus.petren@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Tobias G.", "Köllner", email = "koellner@ice.mpg.de",
    role = c("aut")),
    person("Robert R.", "Junker", email = "robert.junker@uni-marburg.de",
    role = c("aut")))
Description: Quantify and visualize various measures of chemical diveristy and 
    dissimilarity, for phytochemicals and other sets of chemical composition
    data. Importantly, these measures can incorporate biosynthetic and/or 
    structural properties of the chemical compounds, resulting in more 
    comprehensive quantifications of diversity and dissimilarity. 
